descriptionHtml:
Are you tired of feeling distracted and unproductive at work? The Pomodoro Technique is a time management method that has been proven to help with distractions, hyper-focus, and getting things done in short bursts. And with our app, FocusCommit - Pomodoro Timer, it's even easier to implement this technique into your daily routine.

Our app acts as a Pomodoro timer, breaking up tasks into discrete intervals, with short breaks in between and longer breaks after 4 intervals. You can customize the duration of these intervals, short breaks, and long breaks to fit your specific needs. This way, you can work in focused, productive bursts and still have time to relax and recharge.

But our app offers more than just a Pomodoro timer. It also includes a variety of features to help you manage your projects and tasks, including:

* Task and project management: Organize and keep track of your tasks and projects with ease.
* Statistics by tasks, by project, and by interval: Monitor your progress and productivity over time.
* Kanban Board visualization: Visualize your work, workflow and your to-do list in a clear and easy-to-use format.
* Task management integration with Google Tasks and Microsoft To-Do: Synchronize your tasks across multiple platforms.
* Calendar syncing: Keep your schedule organized and never miss a deadline.
* White noise support: Block out distractions and stay focused with ambient background sounds.
* Windows 10 app support: Use our app on your desktop, as well as your mobile device.

With FocusCommit - Pomodoro Timer, you'll be able to work more efficiently and effectively. Whether you're a student, a professional, or just someone looking to boost their productivity, our app is a great tool for anyone looking to improve their focus and get more done.
